def calculate_max_liked_problems(N: int) -> int:
    MOD = 1000000008
    fib = [2, 3]
    sum_fib = [2, 5]
    for i in range(1, N):
        next_fib = (fib[i] + fib[i - 1]) % MOD
        fib.append(next_fib)
        sum_fib.append((sum_fib[i] + next_fib) % MOD)
    return sum_fib[N - 1]
